ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectLand near Hay River associated with the K'atlodeeche First Nation, Northwest Territories ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder consenting to the RELINQUISHMENT in perpetuity, by the Commissioner of the Northwest Territories, of the administration and control of the surface and subsurface rights of 3 parcels of land, being reserve lands associated with the K'ATLODEECHE FIRST NATION located near the community of Hay River in the Northwest Territories that were originally transferred to the Commissioner of Northwest Territories under the Northwest Territories Lands and Resources Devolution Transfer Agreement on April 1, 2014.
AttachmentsAttachment
